channel.title: What videos would you like to view?
channel.description:
I'm starting to create runescape videos once again, it's been a good year maybe even two years since I last recorded a series for youtube so I thought I should start it back up again and see how it goes.
I have a few ideas in mind, but I would like to hear what you guys think. If I get a lot of ideas I will change the topic to a runescape movie development and recruit members from this forum to participate. So, let me know what runescape video would attract your attention!
